snippet.title: Grit v0.0.4 - Hardcore Permadeath Survival
snippet.description:
https://xpndsprt.itch.io/grit
Slowly a memory of a crash comes back to you.  You remember being flung out of your seat and into the cold, dark ocean...  You stand up, shake off the sand and look around, realizing how truly, deeply, and totally flonked you are.
